### POST accept a friend request from another user
### This is the id filed of friendship
@cancelId = e976f12a-552a-41fa-8d9d-d0bc9cb06f1a
POST http://localhost:8080/api/friends/requests/{{cancelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

### POST accept a friend request from another user
### This is the id filed of friendship
@acceptId = e976f12a-552a-41fa-8d9d-d0bc9cb06f1a
POST http://localhost:8080/api/friends/requests/{{acceptId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

### POST decline a friend request from another user
### This is the id filed of friendship
@declineId = e976f12a-552a-41fa-8d9d-d0bc9cb06f1a
POST http://localhost:8080/api/friends/requests/{{declineId}}/decline
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

### DELETE remove a friend
### Note the id is requester_id of friendship
@friendId = 5116e831-ec5a-4127-979a-768ac27b8b2b
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/friends/{{friendId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

